23
00:03:10,002 --> 00:03:11,687
Sta bi to moglo biti?

24
00:03:12,266 --> 00:03:14,648
Sigurno je egzekucija
Shibatainih spijuna.

25
00:03:15,807 --> 00:03:19,623
Moram prodati sve ovo pre borbe.

26
00:03:19,826 --> 00:03:22,239
- Mozes li prodati u Nagahami?
- Da.

27
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:27,030
Cuo sam da je biznis u
razvitku od kako je dosao Hashiba.

28
00:03:27,225 --> 00:03:30,378
- Mogu li ja sa tobom?
- Ne, ne zeno.

29
00:03:30,573 --> 00:03:33,433
Ne znas nasta su
sve spremni razbojnici.

30
00:03:33,636 --> 00:03:38,670
Osim toga, moras ostati i
brinuti se za malu Genichi.

31
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,121
Idi ako moras!

32
00:03:41,704 --> 00:03:44,510
Kakav ces samuraj postati!
Budalo!

33
00:03:44,703 --> 00:03:46,769
Koliko covek moze
porasti bez velikih snova?

34
00:03:46,967 --> 00:03:49,512
Ambicija mora biti
beskrajna kao okean.

35
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:53,947
Sanjalice!
Ni mac ne znas da drzis.

36
00:03:55,069 --> 00:03:57,961
Drzi se trgovine da ne bi zazalio.

37
00:03:58,163 --> 00:03:59,782
Samo cekaj dok se ne obogatim.

38
00:03:59,981 --> 00:04:04,026
Kunem se Bogom Rata:
Dosta mi je vise sirotinje.

39
00:04:04,222 --> 00:04:06,223
Genjuro,
povedi me sa sobom, molim te.

40
00:04:06,424 --> 00:04:08,804
Zaboravi na svoje glupe snove.

41
00:04:09,006 --> 00:04:12,540
- Dozvoli mi da vucem kola.
- Prestani budalo!

42
00:04:12,738 --> 00:04:14,108
U zabludi je.

43
00:04:14,300 --> 00:04:17,106
Misli da ga ceka
velika buducnost u Nagahami.

44
00:04:17,362 --> 00:04:18,884
kakva glupost!

45
00:04:19,085 --> 00:04:20,966
Miyagi, otisao sam.

46
00:04:43,485 --> 00:04:46,029
Previse su pohlepni.

47
00:04:46,227 --> 00:04:49,119
Ne samo Tobei. Genjuro takodje.

48
00:04:49,576 --> 00:04:54,992
Brzi profit stecen u
haoticno vreme ne traje dugo.

49
00:04:55,827 --> 00:04:58,634
Malo novca rasplamsa covekovu pozudu.

50
00:05:00,261 --> 00:05:04,045
Bolje da su se pripremili
za nadolazeci rat.

51
00:05:05,747 --> 00:05:08,835
kazi to Genjuro-u kada se vrati.

52
00:05:12,285 --> 00:05:14,167
Hvala na savetima.

53
00:05:21,215 --> 00:05:22,900
Tata se vratio!

54
00:05:26,733 --> 00:05:28,288
Dobrodosao.

55
00:05:30,273 --> 00:05:31,698
Evo.

56
00:05:36,205 --> 00:05:38,532
- Sta je to?
- A sta mislis?

57
00:05:38,916 --> 00:05:41,689
Dobio si to za robu?

58
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,876
Samo oseti.

59
00:05:45,168 --> 00:05:49,049
Nikad nisi videlo toliko, zar ne?
Pozurio sam nazad da ti pokazem.

60
00:05:52,217 --> 00:05:55,501
To ja zovem trgovinom!
Sad razumes?

61
00:06:00,542 --> 00:06:02,161
A Tobei?

62
00:06:02,358 --> 00:06:06,404
Naleteo je na samuraja u gradu.

63
00:06:06,792 --> 00:06:09,749
Pokusao sam da ga zaustavim,
ali je otisao za samurajem.

64
00:06:39,006 --> 00:06:41,267
Preklinjem vas, Gospodine!

65
00:06:44,492 --> 00:06:46,079
Dopustite mi da vam sluzim!

66
00:06:46,277 --> 00:06:48,473
Verno cu vas sluziti do smrti!

67
00:06:48,670 --> 00:06:53,770
- Da prihvati prosjaka kao slugu?
- Prvo nabavi neki oklop!

68
00:06:53,964 --> 00:06:57,085
- Oklop i koplje!
- Gubi se, prosjace!

69
00:06:57,281 --> 00:06:59,825
Mogu li onda biti samuraj?

70
00:07:12,049 --> 00:07:14,049
Opet ti?

71
00:07:14,249 --> 00:07:16,217
Nabavi oklop i koplje!

72
00:07:27,676 --> 00:07:30,384
Divno izgledas!
Jesi li srecna?

73
00:07:32,844 --> 00:07:34,594
Da, Veoma lepo.

74
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:41,769
Kao da su se Bon Festival
i Nova Godina spojile.

75
00:07:44,165 --> 00:07:49,483
4 godine vec zelim da ti kupim kimono,
ali nisam mogao da priustim.

76
00:07:49,747 --> 00:07:51,911
Sad konacno mogu!

77
00:07:53,064 --> 00:07:55,511
Sta mislis?
Izgledas srecno.

78
00:07:57,753 --> 00:08:00,264
Nije do kimona,

79
00:08:00,464 --> 00:08:02,976
tvoja dobrota me cini srecnim.

80
00:08:06,173 --> 00:08:10,892
Nista mi nije potrebno
sve dok si tu pored mene.

81
00:08:17,974 --> 00:08:19,975
Vidi.

82
00:08:21,291 --> 00:08:25,749
Susena riba, ulje, brasno, zelenis
i kolaci od rize.

83
00:08:27,415 --> 00:08:29,676
Novac je sve.

84
00:08:29,870 --> 00:08:32,479
Bez njega zivot je tezak,

85
00:08:33,250 --> 00:08:35,284
i nada umire.

86
00:08:38,514 --> 00:08:42,080
Tata mora da radi.

87
00:08:42,278 --> 00:08:44,180
Idemo.

88
00:08:45,243 --> 00:08:47,440
Naucicu jos vise.

89
00:08:49,102 --> 00:08:51,549
Napravicu sto vise grncarija.

90
00:08:52,929 --> 00:08:58,062
Ta mala gomila od prosli put
mi je donela 3 srebrnjaka.

91
00:08:58,257 --> 00:09:01,594
To je dosta.
Sad imamo dosta novca.

92
00:09:02,147 --> 00:09:07,432
Sef sela je rekao da Shibataine trupe
mogu biti ovde vec sutra.

93
00:09:07,633 --> 00:09:09,535
Treba da budemo na oprezu.

94
00:09:09,738 --> 00:09:12,479
Gluposti!
Rat je dobar za biznis.

95
00:09:12,672 --> 00:09:14,292
Vidi koliko sam zaradio!

96
00:09:14,490 --> 00:09:18,601
Jednom si imao srece.
Mozda sledeci put neces imati.

97
00:09:19,211 --> 00:09:21,538
Ako ti se nesto desi...

98
00:09:21,730 --> 00:09:23,219
Prestani da mislis na najgore.

99
00:09:23,421 --> 00:09:25,171
Ah, Ohama.

100
00:09:26,418 --> 00:09:28,039
Genjuro.

101
00:09:28,301 --> 00:09:29,986
Ne brini.

102
00:09:30,183 --> 00:09:33,402
Ni jedan samuraj ne bi
unajmio seljaka u krpama.

103
00:09:33,914 --> 00:09:36,296
Ne brini. Vratice se on.

104
00:09:36,497 --> 00:09:38,248
Uzmi nesto da popijes.

105
00:09:48,363 --> 00:09:49,917
Budalo!

106
00:09:50,945 --> 00:09:53,043
Jesi li dosao razumu?

107
00:09:53,242 --> 00:09:55,308
Izgledas kao prosjak!

108
00:09:55,825 --> 00:09:58,151
Postao si seoski idiot!

109
00:10:19,874 --> 00:10:21,592
Nastavi.

110
00:10:24,785 --> 00:10:27,678
Izvedi ga napolje!
Smeta.

111
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:30,206
Necemo uspeti ako ne pozurimo.

112
00:10:30,590 --> 00:10:33,428
Skloni se, odmah.

113
00:10:36,012 --> 00:10:37,947
Mama, gladan sam.

114
00:10:38,691 --> 00:10:40,659
Kakva maza!

115
00:10:41,146 --> 00:10:43,789
Hajde, jos samo par obrtaja.

116
00:10:48,993 --> 00:10:51,375
Promenio si se.

117
00:10:52,215 --> 00:10:54,096
Uvek razdrazljiv.

118
00:10:54,671 --> 00:10:59,836
Samo zelim da radimo
u miru kao muz i zena

119
00:11:00,508 --> 00:11:03,530
i da troje nas zivimo srecno.

120
00:11:04,525 --> 00:11:06,788
To je sve sto zelim.

121
00:11:39,865 --> 00:11:41,833
Ovaj put si se bas naradio.

122
00:11:42,033 --> 00:11:44,230
Zato sto imam planove.

123
00:11:49,274 --> 00:11:52,776
Hajde da ovu gomilu prodamo u Nagahami.
Obogaticemo se.

124
00:11:53,292 --> 00:11:54,880
Hocu li i ja dobiti deo?

125
00:11:55,078 --> 00:11:57,623
Naravno.
Trecinu svega sto prodamo.

126
00:11:58,554 --> 00:12:02,317
Jedva cekam da se dokopam novca.

127
00:12:07,772 --> 00:12:11,915
Nikad ih nisam videla da toliko rade

128
00:12:14,725 --> 00:12:16,541
Sve su ubacili u pecnicu:

129
00:12:18,106 --> 00:12:22,662
Snagu, duse,
sve.

130
00:12:24,102 --> 00:12:28,212
Sta ce biti ako propadnu?

131
00:12:29,015 --> 00:12:32,299
Ziveti zajedno kao srecna
familija je za mene dovoljno.

132
00:12:33,351 --> 00:12:37,809
Ali on insistira na riziku.
Jednostavno nece da slusa.

133
00:12:38,519 --> 00:12:41,292
Ranije nije bio takav.

134
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:44,350
Rat promeni coveka.

135
00:12:44,547 --> 00:12:47,634
Ipak pokusavaju da
doprinesu zarade novca.

136
00:12:49,171 --> 00:12:50,573
Sta je to?

137
00:12:55,806 --> 00:12:58,829
Probudi se!

138
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:04,475
Glasine su istinite.
Sigurno su Shibataine trupe!

139
00:13:14,144 --> 00:13:15,514
Vidis li sta, Tobei?

140
00:13:15,707 --> 00:13:19,241
Seljani se rasipaju kao pauci!

141
00:13:20,938 --> 00:13:23,678
- Sta cemo?
- Pec mora raditi.

142
00:13:23,872 --> 00:13:26,960
Bicu proklet ako dopustim
da se vatra ugasi.

143
00:13:27,158 --> 00:13:30,529
Haraju po kucama i okupljaju muskarce.

144
00:13:32,357 --> 00:13:33,813
Genichi!

145
00:13:41,223 --> 00:13:43,897
To je Shibataina vojska!
Pozuri, trci!

146
00:13:45,402 --> 00:13:47,663
Cekaj!

147
00:14:00,901 --> 00:14:05,262
Regrutujemo muskarce!
Ne pokusavajte pobeci!

148
00:14:06,993 --> 00:14:08,582
Ovo je strasno!

149
00:14:09,034 --> 00:14:11,263
Bezite!
Shibataine trupe!

150
00:14:12,415 --> 00:14:15,221
Kradu sve!
Sakrite rizu i ostale dragocenosti!

151
00:14:16,531 --> 00:14:18,379
Ne dozvolite im da vam uzmu zene!

152
00:14:19,975 --> 00:14:22,997
Regrutuju sve muskarce.

153
00:14:24,567 --> 00:14:26,285
Kakva banda vukova!

154
00:14:27,151 --> 00:14:29,445
Da su samo sacekali jos jednu noc!

155
00:14:30,340 --> 00:14:33,591
Pozuri!
Isuvise je opasno ovde.

156
00:14:33,785 --> 00:14:34,861
Pozuri!

157
00:14:35,061 --> 00:14:38,366
Ako izgubimo ovu gomilu,
necu dobiti svoj deo od profita!

158
00:14:41,694 --> 00:14:44,207
Izgubices glavu za taj kiln!

159
00:14:44,405 --> 00:14:48,321
Hajde, pozuri!

160
00:14:48,712 --> 00:14:52,442
Skuvaj malo rize.
Trebace nam u planinama.

161
00:14:53,304 --> 00:14:55,783
Ohama, pozuri!

162
00:14:57,865 --> 00:14:59,681
Majko!

163
00:15:14,737 --> 00:15:17,955
Pokusavate da se sakrijete, eh?
Izlazi!

164
00:15:21,084 --> 00:15:22,802
Upomoc!

165
00:15:32,853 --> 00:15:35,909
Molim vas, ostavite nas na miru
ili cemo izgladneti!

166
00:15:36,106 --> 00:15:38,650
Preklinjemo vas!

167
00:15:44,621 --> 00:15:46,525
Skloni se!

168
00:15:48,162 --> 00:15:51,055
Skloni se budalo!

169
00:16:43,914 --> 00:16:45,469
Spremno je.

170
00:16:51,632 --> 00:16:53,252
Hvala.

171
00:16:56,097 --> 00:16:57,879
Pozuri i jedi.

172
00:17:01,008 --> 00:17:02,596
Sta se desilo Tobeiu?

173
00:17:02,795 --> 00:17:04,578
Kakva budala.

174
00:17:10,481 --> 00:17:12,199
Jeste li videli mog muza?

175
00:17:12,394 --> 00:17:14,145
Nisam.

176
00:17:44,831 --> 00:17:46,038
Ko je tamo?

177
00:18:03,426 --> 00:18:05,721
Stisalo se dole.

178
00:18:06,137 --> 00:18:08,518
Puske se vise ne cuju

179
00:18:20,649 --> 00:18:22,204
Genjuro, kuda ces?

180
00:18:22,403 --> 00:18:25,840
Suvise je opasno.
Sacekaj da vojnici odu.

181
00:18:26,039 --> 00:18:27,790
Bolje je da sacekas.

182
00:18:27,984 --> 00:18:30,181
Ne mogu da cekam! Moram ici!

183
00:18:30,377 --> 00:18:33,150
- Molim te, nemoj!
- Ne mogu ti to dopustiti!

184
00:18:33,343 --> 00:18:36,333
Zaboravi na pec!
Sta ako te uhvate?

185
00:18:36,533 --> 00:18:37,935
Vatra!

186
00:18:38,127 --> 00:18:41,857
Uvek mozemo napraviti jos.

187
00:18:42,050 --> 00:18:44,595
Tisina!
Ne mogu dozvoliti da propadnu.

188
00:19:06,195 --> 00:19:08,195
Prokletstvo!
Vatra se ugasila!

189
00:19:16,528 --> 00:19:17,669
Genjuro!

190
00:19:17,867 --> 00:19:20,227
Prekasno.
Vatra se ugasila.

191
00:19:31,455 --> 00:19:33,010
Prazno je!

192
00:19:36,047 --> 00:19:36,972
Sta je?

193
00:19:37,164 --> 00:19:40,220
- Jel neko unutra?
- Mozda je nesto skriveno unutra.

194
00:19:40,417 --> 00:19:42,265
Proveri.

195
00:20:02,328 --> 00:20:04,655
Nista, samo grncarija.

196
00:20:05,677 --> 00:20:06,916
Hajdemo.

197
00:20:34,670 --> 00:20:36,486
Gotovi su!

198
00:20:38,688 --> 00:20:41,047
Vidi! Peceni su!

199
00:20:42,164 --> 00:20:44,839
Hvala bogu!

200
00:20:45,035 --> 00:20:47,101
Gotovi su!

201
00:20:50,936 --> 00:20:52,555
Jesu li peceni?

202
00:20:52,817 --> 00:20:55,840
Jesu!
I to dobro.

203
00:20:56,038 --> 00:20:57,755
Pozuri i natovari.

204
00:20:58,015 --> 00:20:59,701
Znaci idemo u Nagahamu?

205
00:20:59,898 --> 00:21:02,345
Nemoguce je sad.
Ici cemo preko jezera.

206
00:21:02,544 --> 00:21:04,394
Ohamina cerka je camdzija.

207
00:21:04,586 --> 00:21:06,750
Ti ces veslati?

208
00:21:06,978 --> 00:21:08,946
Mozemo li sigurno stici do reke?

209
00:21:09,146 --> 00:21:10,963
Ici cemo precicom.

210
00:21:11,156 --> 00:21:12,744
Gde cemo naci brod?

211
00:21:12,942 --> 00:21:15,172
Tamo uvek ima napustenih brodova.

212
00:21:15,366 --> 00:21:17,693
Pozuri, hajde da ispraznimo pec.

213
00:22:21,101 --> 00:22:26,038
U vodama Azuchia

214
00:22:26,364 --> 00:22:34,302
Mali camac plovi

215
00:22:40,939 --> 00:22:46,832
Svi su zaspali

216
00:22:47,445 --> 00:22:50,370
Padaju preko kormila

217
00:22:52,708 --> 00:22:55,122
Magla je bas gusta.

218
00:22:57,843 --> 00:23:01,692
Genichi, ovo je jezero.
Zar nije lepo?

219
00:23:03,233 --> 00:23:05,398
Konacno smo van opasnosti.

220
00:23:06,359 --> 00:23:09,316
Dobro je sto smo krenuli brodom.

221
00:23:09,803 --> 00:23:12,728
Umakli smo za dlaku.

222
00:23:12,928 --> 00:23:15,061
Stizemo u Omizo do jutra.

223
00:23:15,544 --> 00:23:19,143
To je tamo gde Lord Niwa
ima dvorac.

224
00:23:19,946 --> 00:23:22,273
Jos bolje nego u Nagahami.

225
00:23:22,752 --> 00:23:25,427
Bicemo bogati,

226
00:23:26,102 --> 00:23:28,809
i nase zene ce biti bogate.

227
00:23:31,332 --> 00:23:33,812
Napravicu stovariste u nasem selu.

228
00:23:34,362 --> 00:23:36,656
A ja cu kupiti samurajski oklop.

229
00:23:37,711 --> 00:23:42,202
Ovaj svet je privremeno boraviste

230
00:23:44,026 --> 00:23:49,442
Gde jecajima docekujemo zoru
Uzdrmani talasima

231
00:24:07,246 --> 00:24:08,517
To je camac.

232
00:24:20,449 --> 00:24:22,297
Duh jezera!

233
00:24:23,288 --> 00:24:25,898
Ne, nisam duh.

234
00:24:28,136 --> 00:24:30,583
Ja sam camdzija iz Kaizua.

235
00:24:32,696 --> 00:24:36,329
Krenuo sam u Azuchi sa mojim tovarom,

236
00:24:37,034 --> 00:24:38,915
kada su me presreli pirati.

237
00:24:41,308 --> 00:24:42,732
Vode.

238
00:24:43,892 --> 00:24:45,033
Dajte mi vode!

239
00:24:51,260 --> 00:24:52,303
Hvala vam.

240
00:25:04,081 --> 00:25:07,680
Gde god da ste krenuli,

241
00:25:08,578 --> 00:25:10,035
pazite se pirata.

242
00:25:11,671 --> 00:25:13,552
Ako vas vide,

243
00:25:13,745 --> 00:25:17,246
izubicete vas tovar i vase zivote.

244
00:25:18,848 --> 00:25:20,849
Pazite na zene.

245
00:25:21,399 --> 00:25:22,736
Zene!

246
00:25:36,517 --> 00:25:38,072
Milostivi Buda.

247
00:25:41,939 --> 00:25:44,201
Buda, smiluj se na njegovoj dusi.

248
00:25:50,264 --> 00:25:54,657
Hajdemo nazad.
Ovo je los znak.

249
00:25:58,907 --> 00:26:02,212
Hajde da vratimo zenu na obalu.
Nastavicemo sami.

250
00:26:02,416 --> 00:26:03,689
Molim vas ne idite.

251
00:26:03,883 --> 00:26:05,916
Idem i ja,
da pazim na Tobeia.

252
00:26:06,115 --> 00:26:08,441
- Kidnapuju zene.
- Rizikovacu.

253
00:26:08,635 --> 00:26:11,821
Idem svuda gde i ti.
Molim te povedi me sa sobom.

254
00:26:12,016 --> 00:26:15,071
- Moras se brinuti o Genichi.
- Molim te, povedi me!

255
00:26:15,556 --> 00:26:18,993
Ohama, vrati nas na obalu.
Brzo!

256
00:26:40,370 --> 00:26:42,251
Vraticemo se cim zaradimo novac.

257
00:26:42,443 --> 00:26:45,303
Vracamo se za desetak dana.
Cekajte nas.

258
00:26:48,215 --> 00:26:51,684
Ne pokusavjte da se borite
ako vas pirati napadnu.

259
00:26:53,032 --> 00:26:55,326
Znam.
Nemojte ici glavnim putem.

260
00:26:55,519 --> 00:26:58,607
Zapamti: Idite planinskim putem.

261
00:26:58,805 --> 00:27:01,729
I nemojte odmah ici kuci.
Razumes?

262
00:27:01,930 --> 00:27:05,563
?v? nesreca nece dugo trajati.
Budi strpljiva.

263
00:27:07,991 --> 00:27:10,829
Tobei, Ohama...
molim te pazi na njega.

264
00:27:11,531 --> 00:27:14,042
Ne brini.
uskoro se vracamo.

265
00:27:14,242 --> 00:27:15,829
Dobro se staraj o Genichiu.

266
00:27:16,028 --> 00:27:19,432
Bicete iznenadjeni kada se
vratimo sa svim tim srebrom.

267
00:27:20,111 --> 00:27:21,959
Tata!

268
00:27:34,112 --> 00:27:36,145
Molim te cuvaj se!

269
00:27:38,354 --> 00:27:40,171
Vrati se nazad ziv i zdrav!

270
00:27:49,676 --> 00:27:52,351
- Tata!
- Cuvaj se!

271
00:27:57,554 --> 00:27:59,652
Tata!

272
00:29:08,168 --> 00:29:10,017
Uzecu tu vazu.

273
00:29:10,210 --> 00:29:12,373
Ovu?

274
00:29:13,239 --> 00:29:17,154
Tu bocu za sake i te case.

275
00:29:21,404 --> 00:29:25,667
I te cinije za rizu,
ploce i boce.

276
00:29:28,070 --> 00:29:31,191
Cinije za rizu, ploce i boce.

277
00:29:31,547 --> 00:29:36,168
Zivimo u Kutsuki Manor.
Molim vas da ih tamo dostavite.

278
00:29:37,734 --> 00:29:40,443
Platicemo vam po isporuci.

279
00:29:41,083 --> 00:29:42,768
Hvala vam.

280
00:29:57,477 --> 00:30:00,565
- Dvorska straza!
- Prolaz!

281
00:30:02,835 --> 00:30:05,696
Ne gledaj!
Dobices sulude ideje!

282
00:30:05,897 --> 00:30:06,973
Umukni!

283
00:30:11,127 --> 00:30:13,063
Sa oklopom bih mogao biti samuraj.

284
00:30:13,424 --> 00:30:15,718
Mac. Koplje. Oklop.

285
00:30:15,912 --> 00:30:18,457
Ne razbacuj se sa nasim
tesko zaradjenim novcem.

286
00:30:18,654 --> 00:30:21,264
- Ostavi me, idiote!
- Zaustavite ga!

287
00:30:22,323 --> 00:30:25,857
Pusti me! Sledeci put
kada se vidimo bicu samuraj!

288
00:30:26,469 --> 00:30:28,219
Molim te, zaustavi ga!

289
00:30:29,148 --> 00:30:30,800
Tobei!

290
00:30:45,765 --> 00:30:47,189
otisla je.

291
00:30:47,583 --> 00:30:48,856
Mogu li vam pomoci?

292
00:30:49,050 --> 00:30:50,323
Jedan oklop.

293
00:31:08,283 --> 00:31:10,608
Da li izgledam kao samuraj?

294
00:31:10,802 --> 00:31:12,422
Da, i to dobar.

295
00:31:12,620 --> 00:31:14,501
Ali ti je potrebno i koplje.

296
00:31:14,693 --> 00:31:16,117
Uzecu jedno!

297
00:31:19,286 --> 00:31:20,459
Izvoli.

298
00:31:27,228 --> 00:31:28,304
Koliko?

299
00:31:31,470 --> 00:31:32,840
Jedan srebrenjak.

300
00:32:01,003 --> 00:32:02,276
Lepa je, zar ne?

301
00:32:05,022 --> 00:32:06,925
Sta to radite?

302
00:32:19,949 --> 00:32:21,319
Prokletnici!

303
00:32:21,832 --> 00:32:23,734
Ubice!

304
00:33:26,034 --> 00:33:27,916
Evo ti nesto novca.

305
00:34:06,029 --> 00:34:07,550
Budalo!

306
00:34:10,877 --> 00:34:13,933
Vidi sta sam postala.

307
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:17,475
Jesi li sad zadovoljan,
da vidis svoju osramocenu zenu?

308
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:23,276
Ali sta tebe briga?
Ti si srecan sto si samuraj.

309
00:34:24,656 --> 00:34:27,016
Tobei, budalo bedna!

310
00:34:28,930 --> 00:34:31,093
Velika budalo!

311
00:34:59,388 --> 00:35:03,173
Hoces li pripaziti na moj
box dok mi se partner ne vrati?

312
00:35:03,376 --> 00:35:06,149
Trebao bi doci uskoro.
Hvala ti.

313
00:35:34,536 --> 00:35:37,146
Gospodine, koliko je jedna?

314
00:35:37,981 --> 00:35:39,982
Hoces li kupiti?

315
00:35:40,724 --> 00:35:43,105
Zavisi od cene.

316
00:35:43,435 --> 00:35:47,284
Previse su raskosne
za zenu coveka kao sto si ti.

317
00:35:47,486 --> 00:35:49,106
Imam novac.

318
00:36:46,585 --> 00:36:48,141
Izvinite.

319
00:36:50,731 --> 00:36:55,028
Pomislile smo da vam
treba vodic da bi nasli put.

320
00:36:55,293 --> 00:36:58,131
Vrlo ste ljubazni.

321
00:37:03,362 --> 00:37:05,395
Pratite nas.

322
00:38:27,148 --> 00:38:29,442
Udjite molim vas.

323
00:38:31,805 --> 00:38:34,665
Hvala, ali bih trebao da krenem.

324
00:38:35,346 --> 00:38:38,978
Dama Wakasa vas ceka.
Udjite molim vas.

325
00:38:40,736 --> 00:38:44,716
Da li mislite na mladu damu?

326
00:38:44,914 --> 00:38:47,904
Da, Cerku nedavnog Lorda Kutsuki.

327
00:38:48,549 --> 00:38:52,182
Udjite sad molim vas.
Nema potrebe da se stidite.

328
00:39:33,106 --> 00:39:35,042
Hvala vam.

329
00:39:42,770 --> 00:39:44,423
Udjite.

330
00:41:06,301 --> 00:41:08,367
Ovuda.

331
00:41:19,824 --> 00:41:24,119
Vi ste majstor Genjuro
iz Omi provincije, zat ne?

332
00:41:27,926 --> 00:41:30,764
kako to da znate moje ime?

333
00:41:31,881 --> 00:41:36,469
Kada sam videla vasu keramiku na pijaci,

334
00:41:37,494 --> 00:41:40,202
nisam mogla poverovati svojim ocima.

335
00:41:40,683 --> 00:41:43,488
Plave posude bljestave

336
00:41:43,682 --> 00:41:46,606
kao kristali.

337
00:41:48,753 --> 00:41:51,362
Otac me je ucio

338
00:41:51,879 --> 00:41:54,520
da cenim takve stvari.

339
00:41:56,088 --> 00:41:58,829
Htela sam vas upoznati

340
00:41:59,022 --> 00:42:02,905
i da vas pitam kako uspevate
da napravite tako nesto.

341
00:42:03,392 --> 00:42:06,577
To je verovatno tajna?

342
00:42:07,825 --> 00:42:11,076
Ne, nema tajne.

343
00:42:11,748 --> 00:42:13,912
Ali su potrebne godine iskustva

344
00:42:14,109 --> 00:42:17,578
da bi ste naucili.

345
00:42:18,989 --> 00:42:21,500
Plod iskustva je predivan,

346
00:42:22,082 --> 00:42:27,183
ali samo dobar majstor
moze napraviti tako lepo.

347
00:42:27,376 --> 00:42:29,225
Hvala vam.

348
00:42:56,081 --> 00:42:59,387
Nije li ovo moja roba?

349
00:43:02,779 --> 00:43:07,401
Zelim probati sake iz vese solje.

350
00:43:09,988 --> 00:43:13,272
Imate srece, mali moji,
da vas je ova plemenita dama spazila.

351
00:43:16,110 --> 00:43:20,059
Ja sam farmer,
tako da mi je ovo sporedni posao.

352
00:43:20,257 --> 00:43:24,651
Ali na svoje kreacije gledam kao na decu.

353
00:43:25,967 --> 00:43:28,326
Da ih tako plemenita dama koristi

354
00:43:28,518 --> 00:43:30,236
je velika cast.

355
00:43:31,420 --> 00:43:36,640
Da ih vidim u tako lepoj kuci,

356
00:43:37,321 --> 00:43:41,170
dodiravani od strane prelepe dame,

357
00:43:42,328 --> 00:43:44,590
snovi su se obistinili.

358
00:43:44,784 --> 00:43:45,828
Ne, uopste.

359
00:43:46,028 --> 00:43:49,116
Mora da su tuzne od dodira
jedne zene koja je u teskom periodu

360
00:43:49,728 --> 00:43:52,469
kao sto sam ja.

361
00:43:54,097 --> 00:43:55,587
Uzmite molim vas.

362
00:43:58,626 --> 00:44:02,704
Moje solje nikada nisu lepse izgledale.

363
00:44:12,787 --> 00:44:17,279
Vrednost ljudi i stvari zaista
ovisi od toga gde su smesteni.

364
00:44:18,433 --> 00:44:22,925
Moji proizvodi su zaista imali srece.

365
00:44:23,568 --> 00:44:28,788
Tvoj talenat ne sme biti skriven
u nekom siromasnom selu.

366
00:44:29,660 --> 00:44:35,108
Moras pojacati
i iskoristiti tvoj talenat.

367
00:44:38,080 --> 00:44:41,418
Kako to da izvedem?

368
00:44:43,023 --> 00:44:47,286
Tako sto ces se zakleti
na vecnu ljubav Dami Wakasa

369
00:44:47,489 --> 00:44:49,490
i odmah je ozeniti.

370
00:45:55,839 --> 00:46:04,353
Najfinija svila

371
00:46:06,236 --> 00:46:14,457
Retke boje

372
00:46:17,016 --> 00:46:26,869
Moze se promeniti i izlizati

373
00:46:37,460 --> 00:46:48,074
kao moj zivot

374
00:46:48,591 --> 00:46:56,301
Voljeni

375
00:46:59,371 --> 00:47:13,978
Ako si si ti neveran

376
00:47:25,908 --> 00:47:33,237
Nasa ljubavna zakletva

377
00:47:46,607 --> 00:47:55,536
Je zapecacena ovom casom

378
00:48:28,070 --> 00:48:31,321
Njegov glas zvuci tako zadovljno!

379
00:48:35,150 --> 00:48:38,521
To je glas moga oca.

380
00:48:47,015 --> 00:48:51,755
Zbog Nobunaga Oda,

381
00:48:52,278 --> 00:48:55,366
tog gnusnog Nobunaga Oda,

382
00:48:56,265 --> 00:48:59,005
kuca Kutsuki je plakala.

383
00:48:59,199 --> 00:49:03,277
Jedini preziveli je Dama Wakasa

384
00:49:03,472 --> 00:49:06,245
i ja, njena (medicinska) sestra.

385
00:49:06,949 --> 00:49:12,843
Ali duh njenog oca se zadrzao u kuci

386
00:49:13,583 --> 00:49:19,825
i peva ovako svaki put
kada moja Dama igra.

387
00:49:22,450 --> 00:49:26,691
Nije li divan glas?

388
00:49:29,786 --> 00:49:34,722
Odusevljen je veridbom.

389
00:49:46,753 --> 00:49:50,450
Kad god cujem njegov glas...

390
00:51:16,632 --> 00:51:19,013
Jos je rano da bi ustali.

391
00:51:19,215 --> 00:51:20,803
Spavaj koliko god zelis.

392
00:51:21,001 --> 00:51:23,514
Sta radim ja ovde?

393
00:51:25,881 --> 00:51:27,914
Sta to pricate...

394
00:51:29,389 --> 00:51:32,379
kao da ste sve zaboravili.

395
00:51:39,276 --> 00:51:41,985
Moj gospodar se probudio?

396
00:51:44,125 --> 00:51:49,345
Uzmi muza za ruku i odvedi ga na kupanje.

397
00:51:51,556 --> 00:51:55,090
Necu vam smetati.

398
00:52:19,240 --> 00:52:21,817
Izgledas nepoverljivo.

399
00:52:23,387 --> 00:52:27,943
Mislis da sam carobnica,
zar ne?

400
00:52:34,518 --> 00:52:39,205
Ali sad si moj.

401
00:52:45,298 --> 00:52:51,030
Od sad mi moras poveriti svoj zivot.

402
00:53:23,891 --> 00:53:28,067
Ljubav

403
00:53:29,279 --> 00:53:36,000
izludjuje me

404
00:53:49,947 --> 00:53:53,481
Cak i da si duh ili carobnica,

405
00:53:53,679 --> 00:53:55,974
nikada te necu napustiti.

406
00:53:59,931 --> 00:54:02,888
Nisam ni sanjao da
postoji ovakvo zadovoljstvo.

407
00:54:11,859 --> 00:54:14,915
Ovo je izvanredno! Ovo je raj!

408
00:54:38,075 --> 00:54:41,414
Pomozi mi!

409
00:54:43,754 --> 00:54:45,755
neka mi neko pomogne!

410
00:54:49,717 --> 00:54:52,577
Pomozite mi!

411
00:55:02,380 --> 00:55:04,098
Vidis li negde hranu?

412
00:55:23,557 --> 00:55:25,373
Brzo!

413
00:55:26,907 --> 00:55:30,636
Saberi se.
Podji sa mnom.

414
00:55:44,447 --> 00:55:46,351
Come quickly!

415
00:55:47,096 --> 00:55:49,868
Ponesi ovu rizu,
i ovo takodje.

416
00:55:50,062 --> 00:55:52,541
Hvala vam.
necu zaboraviti vasu ljubaznost.

417
00:55:52,741 --> 00:55:55,666
Bices u redu ako ides sporednim putem.

418
00:55:55,866 --> 00:55:58,476
Levo.

419
00:55:59,502 --> 00:56:01,503
Cuvaj se.

420
00:56:09,294 --> 00:56:11,076
Moje je!

421
00:56:31,109 --> 00:56:32,567
Imas li hrane?

422
00:56:32,768 --> 00:56:35,062
Mrtvi smo gladni.

423
00:56:44,984 --> 00:56:47,310
Ta hrana je za mog sina.

424
00:56:47,503 --> 00:56:50,015
Molim vas ostavite to!

425
00:58:44,014 --> 00:58:45,862
Odseci mi glavu!

426
00:59:47,547 --> 00:59:52,419
Doneo sam ti glavu!
Glavu generala!

427
00:59:53,161 --> 00:59:54,302
Sta je?

428
00:59:54,500 --> 00:59:56,598
Pogledaj!

429
01:00:03,175 --> 01:00:06,231
Nasao si glavu velikog generala.

430
01:00:06,428 --> 01:00:08,787
Ne, nisam je nasao.

431
01:00:08,981 --> 01:00:11,428
Ubio sam ga mojim kopljem!

432
01:00:12,744 --> 01:00:15,485
Ko bi rekao, veliki ratnik Katsuhige Fuwa

433
01:00:15,678 --> 01:00:18,320
je dozvolio da ga obican vojnik ubije?

434
01:00:18,516 --> 01:00:22,365
Bices nagradjen.

435
01:00:22,599 --> 01:00:24,599
Sta zelis?

436
01:00:26,299 --> 01:00:29,040
Konja, oklop i slugu.

437
01:00:29,232 --> 01:00:31,810
Dobro.
Imaces.

438
01:00:33,220 --> 01:00:35,122
Hvala vam!

439
01:00:56,152 --> 01:00:57,772
Ima hod velikog samuraja!

440
01:00:57,970 --> 01:00:59,819
Kom klanu pripada?

441
01:01:00,010 --> 01:01:02,175
Ubio je Fuwa, velikog Generala.

442
01:01:02,721 --> 01:01:03,798
kako se zove?

443
01:01:03,998 --> 01:01:06,835
Tobei od Nakanogoa,
glavni cove Lorda Niwae.

444
01:01:11,780 --> 01:01:16,337
Prelepe devojke cekaju samuraje.

445
01:01:16,661 --> 01:01:19,302
Imamo najbolji sake i ribu.

446
01:01:22,273 --> 01:01:24,785
Ne mogu te pustiti da prodjes.

447
01:01:28,556 --> 01:01:30,372
Sta je ovo?

448
01:01:30,565 --> 01:01:32,120
Sefe, hajde da se odmorimo ovde.

449
01:01:32,320 --> 01:01:35,126
Ne, idem pravo kuci.

450
01:01:35,318 --> 01:01:38,373
Tamo me neko ceka.
Mora me videti u svoj slavi.

451
01:01:38,572 --> 01:01:41,431
Sefe, budi plemenit.
Hajde da proslavimo vas trijumf.

452
01:01:41,633 --> 01:01:43,667
Vasi ljudi se raduju tome.

453
01:01:43,865 --> 01:01:45,866
Vidim. Dobro.

454
01:01:47,565 --> 01:01:52,285
Ja, Tobei Nakanogo
iz vojske Lord Niwa, odmoricu se ovde.

455
01:01:52,477 --> 01:01:53,585
Pripremite stolove.

456
01:01:53,784 --> 01:01:56,013
odmorice se ovde.
Pokazite zahvalnost.

457
01:01:56,208 --> 01:01:57,665
Hvala vam.

458
01:02:08,806 --> 01:02:10,362
Prolaz!

459
01:02:11,455 --> 01:02:14,097
Rascistite put za Gospodara Tobeia!

460
01:02:29,571 --> 01:02:31,321
Dobrodosli.

461
01:02:33,844 --> 01:02:36,900
- Ko je Tobei?
- Tamo.

462
01:02:37,161 --> 01:02:38,466
On?

463
01:02:39,362 --> 01:02:42,070
Cuo sam za njegov podvig.

464
01:02:47,495 --> 01:02:50,746
Mogu li da pijem iz vase solje. gospodine,
pa da vasa sreca predje i na mene?

465
01:02:50,939 --> 01:02:52,015
I ja!

466
01:02:52,215 --> 01:02:55,781
Kako ste uspeli da
ubijete tako velikog ratnika?

467
01:02:55,978 --> 01:02:59,708
Da, recite nam
pa da i mi uradimo tako nesto!

468
01:02:59,902 --> 01:03:02,316
Vodic za buduce akcije!

469
01:03:02,518 --> 01:03:04,583
nema se sta reci.

470
01:03:05,324 --> 01:03:07,999
Treba vam mozak.
treba vam znanje.

471
01:03:08,354 --> 01:03:12,269
Cvrsta ruka.
vestina u borbi.

472
01:03:12,468 --> 01:03:13,805
Borilacke vestine.

473
01:03:14,222 --> 01:03:17,659
Brzina.

474
01:03:17,858 --> 01:03:19,794
Mogucnost da vidite zivot u daljini.

475
01:03:19,995 --> 01:03:23,944
Onda cete biti mudri kao Kongming,
kineski strategist.

476
01:03:24,652 --> 01:03:27,609
Ali pored svega,
biti cistog uma.

477
01:03:28,287 --> 01:03:30,485
Shvatate?
- Zaista.

478
01:03:30,775 --> 01:03:34,244
Za vojnu taktiku,
uciti Kusunoki i Koshu skolu.

479
01:03:34,443 --> 01:03:36,857
Za oruzije,
uciti Kanamaru skolu.

480
01:03:37,122 --> 01:03:39,091
Za koplje,
uciti Otsubo skolu.

481
01:03:39,387 --> 01:03:42,986
Sledece sto trebate znati je
jacanje.

482
01:03:43,724 --> 01:03:45,507
Onda taktiku odbrane,

483
01:03:45,702 --> 01:03:48,888
V-formaciju i tako to.

484
01:03:57,471 --> 01:03:58,547
Hej!

485
01:03:59,098 --> 01:04:00,304
Moj novac!

486
01:04:00,787 --> 01:04:02,245
Pusti me!

487
01:04:05,540 --> 01:04:06,877
Luda kucko!

488
01:04:07,709 --> 01:04:10,122
Zaustavi ga!
Gde si posao?

489
01:04:10,324 --> 01:04:12,684
Pusti me!

490
01:04:12,875 --> 01:04:15,518
Bezis kao lopov!

491
01:04:15,715 --> 01:04:18,292
nemam novca za bludnice poput tebe!

492
01:04:21,391 --> 01:04:24,349
Nitkov!
Ismevas me.

493
01:04:24,932 --> 01:04:26,868
Ovo ce biti dovoljno.

494
01:04:29,780 --> 01:04:31,020
Ohama!

495
01:04:33,575 --> 01:04:35,740
Znaci ti si veliki covek sad.

496
01:04:36,829 --> 01:04:41,287
Konacno postao samuraj iz snova, eh?

497
01:04:45,249 --> 01:04:48,087
Dok si se ti uzdizao,

498
01:04:48,534 --> 01:04:50,284
i ja sam napravila ime.

499
01:04:50,480 --> 01:04:55,515
U mom fensi kimonu i sminci,
pijuci najbolji sake,

500
01:04:55,710 --> 01:04:58,352
svako vece sam sa drugim covekom.

501
01:04:58,740 --> 01:05:01,220
Veliki uspeh za zenu, zar ne?

502
01:05:08,786 --> 01:05:11,168
Sigurno si zadovoljan.
To si oduvek zeleo.

503
01:05:11,371 --> 01:05:14,872
Svaki uspeh ima cenu.

504
01:05:15,549 --> 01:05:19,844
Tvoja zena je mozda pala,
ali tvoj uspeh je veliki.

505
01:05:21,225 --> 01:05:22,366
Dodji!

506
01:05:22,757 --> 01:05:26,389
Budi moja musterija nocas
i onda cemo slaviti.

507
01:05:26,584 --> 01:05:29,889
Kupi ovu propalu zenu sa
slavno zaradjenim novcem!

508
01:05:35,961 --> 01:05:39,658
bez tebe,
moj uspeh mi e znaci nista.

509
01:05:40,044 --> 01:05:41,120
To je laz!

510
01:05:41,319 --> 01:05:44,624
Moja vera ti nije znacila nista,
sve dok nisi postao samuraj.

511
01:05:45,497 --> 01:05:47,465
Ne, gresis.

512
01:05:52,705 --> 01:05:56,272
Mislio sam da ces se ponositi sa mnom.

513
01:05:59,723 --> 01:06:02,778
Nisam ni sanjao o ovome.

514
01:06:03,134 --> 01:06:05,494
Ja sam osramocena zena.

515
01:06:09,451 --> 01:06:11,582
A ti si kriv.

516
01:06:12,830 --> 01:06:16,115
Mozes li mi vratiti cast?
- Mogu.

517
01:06:16,306 --> 01:06:19,330
- Inace nemam drugog izbora sem da umrem!
- Mogu!

518
01:06:19,528 --> 01:06:21,822
Kunem se da cu ti vratiti cast.

519
01:06:22,048 --> 01:06:24,853
Koliko sam samo puta pozelela da umrem,

520
01:06:25,046 --> 01:06:27,428
ali sam te prvo morala videti!

521
01:06:28,108 --> 01:06:32,056
Mrzela sam sebe zbog toga,

522
01:06:32,796 --> 01:06:35,439
ali nisam mogla umreti a da te ne vidim!

523
01:06:58,918 --> 01:07:00,571
Ovo...

524
01:07:02,331 --> 01:07:03,505
i ovo.

525
01:07:04,946 --> 01:07:08,035
Nemam dovoljno.
Mozes li sniziti cenu?

526
01:07:10,081 --> 01:07:13,550
U tom slucaju, uzecu ovo nazad.

527
01:07:13,749 --> 01:07:15,401
Zelim taj.

528
01:07:15,599 --> 01:07:18,589
Dodji u Kutsuki Manor
i platicu ti ostatak.

529
01:07:19,554 --> 01:07:23,121
- Kutsuki Manor?
- Da, na kraju planine.

530
01:07:27,814 --> 01:07:31,186
Uzmi sve i odlazi!

531
01:07:32,376 --> 01:07:34,756
Zadrzi i novac.
Samo idi!

532
01:07:45,835 --> 01:07:47,139
Cekaj.

533
01:07:47,972 --> 01:07:49,309
Postovanje?

534
01:07:49,502 --> 01:07:52,145
Vidim nesto strasno.
Neku bolest.

535
01:07:52,500 --> 01:07:53,805
Sta je?

536
01:07:54,000 --> 01:07:56,359
Da te pogledam izbliza.

537
01:07:56,552 --> 01:07:58,584
- Mene?
- Da, tebe.

538
01:07:59,230 --> 01:08:03,146
Mozemo ovde razgovarati.
Prati me.

539
01:08:12,689 --> 01:08:16,473
Senka smrti ti je na licu.

540
01:08:18,430 --> 01:08:21,932
Da nisi prisao nekom
cudnom stvorenju?

541
01:08:22,896 --> 01:08:24,712
Ne, nisam.

542
01:08:25,511 --> 01:08:30,166
Nemas li porodicu?

543
01:08:34,984 --> 01:08:38,649
Ako neko zavisi od tebe,
vratimu se odmah.

544
01:08:40,023 --> 01:08:42,981
Ako ostanes ovde jos neko vremer,
umreces.

545
01:08:43,627 --> 01:08:45,214
Vrati se kuci odmah.

546
01:08:45,414 --> 01:08:47,034
Ali zasto?

547
01:08:47,232 --> 01:08:50,537
Ne pitaj zasto.
Tvoj zivot je u opasnosti.

548
01:08:52,398 --> 01:08:57,118
Provodim dane srecno sa
Damom Wakasa u Kutsuki Manoru.

549
01:08:57,309 --> 01:08:59,158
Dama Wakasa je duh mrtvih.

550
01:08:59,351 --> 01:09:00,525
Gluposti.

551
01:09:02,317 --> 01:09:06,047
Ta tvoja ljubav je zabranjena.

552
01:09:08,186 --> 01:09:10,284
Zar ne volis zenu i dete?

553
01:09:11,470 --> 01:09:14,080
Hoces da se odreknes zivota
i da napustis i njih?

554
01:09:17,244 --> 01:09:18,484
cekaj.

555
01:09:22,601 --> 01:09:24,766
Idi onda, ako moras.

556
01:09:25,696 --> 01:09:29,741
Ali te ne mogu pustiti u celjust smrti.

557
01:09:31,660 --> 01:09:34,018
isteracu tog demona.

558
01:09:34,881 --> 01:09:36,121
Dodji.

559
01:09:37,274 --> 01:09:40,079
kada shvatis koliko je grozan ovaj duh,

560
01:09:40,272 --> 01:09:43,457
doci ces razumu.

561
01:10:15,323 --> 01:10:16,780
kako je lepo!

562
01:10:23,584 --> 01:10:25,650
Divnog li nakita!

563
01:10:34,300 --> 01:10:35,953
Cinis me tako sretnom!

564
01:10:38,255 --> 01:10:40,582
Tako si brizan!

565
01:10:43,773 --> 01:10:48,546
Dosta si kasnio u povratku
pa sam se zabrinula.

566
01:10:52,225 --> 01:10:54,965
Izgledas mucno.

567
01:10:55,606 --> 01:10:57,356
Sta se desilo?

568
01:11:00,550 --> 01:11:02,137
Sta je?

569
01:11:06,355 --> 01:11:09,660
Ne smes otici.

570
01:11:10,309 --> 01:11:14,289
Od pada naseg klana,

571
01:11:14,487 --> 01:11:17,325
ljudi nas tretiraju sa prezirom

572
01:11:17,996 --> 01:11:21,281
i kaljaju nase ime.

573
01:11:21,791 --> 01:11:23,988
Kakav podao svet!

574
01:11:24,502 --> 01:11:26,123
Genjuro,

575
01:11:26,799 --> 01:11:29,474
zelim da zauvek budes sa mnom.

576
01:11:31,998 --> 01:11:36,174
Hajde da napustimo ovo mesto
i vratimo se u prirodu.

577
01:11:40,066 --> 01:11:44,688
Genjuro,
ti si moj dozivotni suprug.

578
01:11:45,711 --> 01:11:47,593
Zar neces poci sa mnom?

579
01:11:49,316 --> 01:11:50,969
Oprosti mi!

580
01:11:53,016 --> 01:11:54,440
Ja sam...

581
01:11:57,289 --> 01:12:00,790
Lagao sam vas.

582
01:12:02,647 --> 01:12:06,084
Imam zenu i dete.

583
01:12:06,379 --> 01:12:11,382
Ostali su kod kuce u haosu rata.

584
01:12:11,578 --> 01:12:14,568
Molim te zaboravi na to.

585
01:12:14,768 --> 01:12:16,289
Molim te pusti me da idem kuci!

586
01:12:16,777 --> 01:12:18,050
Ne!

587
01:12:18,754 --> 01:12:20,407
ne mozes se vratiti.

588
01:12:30,300 --> 01:12:33,290
Podji sa mnom u moju zemlju.

589
01:12:37,349 --> 01:12:38,806
Brzo.

590
01:12:39,932 --> 01:12:41,520
Sta je bilo?

591
01:12:42,356 --> 01:12:44,966
Ima nesto na kozi!

592
01:12:45,323 --> 01:12:46,302
Na kozi?

593
01:12:46,502 --> 01:12:49,427
Genjuro, da li si...

594
01:12:50,809 --> 01:12:52,081
Da li si...

595
01:12:55,975 --> 01:12:58,617
operi te crteze po kozi.

596
01:13:07,393 --> 01:13:10,765
Zasto si se zenio sa
njom ako si vec bio ozenjen?

597
01:13:10,997 --> 01:13:14,183
kako sam mogao da napravim takvu gresku!

598
01:13:15,718 --> 01:13:19,317
Mozda greska za muskarca,
ali za zenu je mnogo gore.

599
01:13:19,514 --> 01:13:22,090
Molim te oprosti.
Pusti me kuci.

600
01:13:22,288 --> 01:13:24,257
Svakako ne!

601
01:13:26,179 --> 01:13:31,725
Operi te Sanskrite,
te sto se Budi mole, te kletve,

602
01:13:31,984 --> 01:13:34,343
ili ti nikada necemo oprostiti!

603
01:13:38,555 --> 01:13:45,689
kako si mogao da
uradis nesto tako grozno?

604
01:13:47,293 --> 01:13:54,373
Zelim da ostanem sa tobom zauvek.

605
01:13:56,255 --> 01:13:58,104
Vecno.

606
01:14:00,306 --> 01:14:02,949
Dama Wakasa je napustila ovaj svet

607
01:14:03,527 --> 01:14:08,432
ne znajuci sta je to ljubav.

608
01:14:08,789 --> 01:14:12,324
Boli me da gledam njenu tugu.

609
01:14:12,521 --> 01:14:19,275
Zelim da moja Dama dozivi
potpuno zadovoljstvo jedne zene,

610
01:14:20,144 --> 01:14:28,269
zato smo se vratili u ovaj svet.

611
01:14:29,202 --> 01:14:31,561
nase nade su bile okoncane.

612
01:14:31,754 --> 01:14:36,278
Upoznala je coveka kao sto si ti

613
01:14:36,475 --> 01:14:40,552
i nasla ljubav i srecu jednom u zivotu.

614
01:14:40,749 --> 01:14:46,446
I sad posle svega,

615
01:14:46,648 --> 01:14:49,128
ti pricas o povratku kuci,

616
01:14:49,328 --> 01:14:53,307
i da se vise nikad ne vidite.

617
01:14:53,794 --> 01:14:56,567
Zar ti nije tesko da zivis sa saznanjem

618
01:14:56,759 --> 01:15:03,262
da si je upropastio
jedinu sansu srece u zivotu?

619
01:15:03,458 --> 01:15:06,676
Zar ne osecas zaljenje?

620
01:15:07,156 --> 01:15:13,333
Genjuro, izbaci te lose misli

621
01:15:14,142 --> 01:15:19,340
i ostani sa njom zauvek...

622
01:15:19,532 --> 01:15:22,076
Molim te oprosti!

623
01:16:26,701 --> 01:16:28,419
To je taj covek!

624
01:16:28,615 --> 01:16:30,779
hej ti, ustani!

625
01:16:32,698 --> 01:16:36,460
- Sta to radite?
- Besramni lopove!

626
01:16:36,716 --> 01:16:39,870
Ukrao si blago iz hrama.

627
01:16:40,064 --> 01:16:43,121
Gresite!
Nisam nista urao!

628
01:16:43,319 --> 01:16:44,242
Tisina!

629
01:16:44,435 --> 01:16:46,882
Ovaj mac je nestao pre mesec dana.

630
01:16:47,081 --> 01:16:50,518
To je nemoguce!
On pripada Kutsuki Manor.

631
01:16:50,718 --> 01:16:53,393
- Kutsuki Manor?
- Tako je!

632
01:16:55,055 --> 01:16:56,643
Mora da si sanjao.

633
01:16:56,841 --> 01:16:59,386
Ovde je nekad bio Kutsuki Manor
pre nego sto je klan nestao.

634
01:16:59,585 --> 01:17:01,433
laze!

635
01:17:01,625 --> 01:17:04,681
Ukrao si tajni mac?

636
01:17:04,942 --> 01:17:07,073
Sumnjiv je.
Pretresi ga.

637
01:17:10,971 --> 01:17:14,125
To je moj novac!
Vrati!

638
01:17:14,319 --> 01:17:16,678
Da su mirna vremena
bacili bi te u zatvor,

639
01:17:17,254 --> 01:17:19,386
ali Shibataina vojska
je spalila zatvor.

640
01:17:19,582 --> 01:17:22,095
Budi im zahvalan,
srecno kopile.

641
01:19:31,210 --> 01:19:32,482
Miyagi.

642
01:20:00,457 --> 01:20:02,936
Izvini sto me nije bilo tako dugo.

643
01:20:03,137 --> 01:20:04,506
Vratio si se!

644
01:20:05,464 --> 01:20:08,042
Znao sam da ces brinuti.

645
01:20:09,196 --> 01:20:13,274
Tako mi je drago da te vidim.

646
01:20:15,033 --> 01:20:16,589
Genichi?

647
01:20:16,851 --> 01:20:18,221
Spava.

648
01:20:18,509 --> 01:20:21,021
Daj da ga zagrlim.

649
01:20:27,057 --> 01:20:30,461
Genichi, vrati sam se.

650
01:20:31,426 --> 01:20:34,928
Tata se vratio.

651
01:20:40,899 --> 01:20:45,293
Zeleo sam da donesem lepe poklone,

652
01:20:45,492 --> 01:20:47,080
ali ovo je sve sto imam.

653
01:20:47,628 --> 01:20:51,163
Napravio sam strasnu gresku!

654
01:20:51,360 --> 01:20:56,612
ne govori mi dragi.
Vratio si se ziv i zdrav.

655
01:20:59,812 --> 01:21:05,358
sad tek vidim koliko si bila u pravu.
Mozak mi je otkazao.

656
01:21:05,553 --> 01:21:08,228
hajde da ne pricamo vise o tome.

657
01:21:09,604 --> 01:21:11,572
Sigurno si umoran.

658
01:21:13,144 --> 01:21:15,080
Imam malo zgotovljenog sakea.

659
01:21:31,547 --> 01:21:33,994
I ima kuvanog mesa.

660
01:22:19,421 --> 01:22:22,672
osecam se tako rastereceno.

661
01:22:24,907 --> 01:22:27,615
Sake nikada nije bio boljeg ukusa.

662
01:22:32,498 --> 01:22:34,596
Tako je mirno vode.

663
01:22:39,706 --> 01:22:43,435
Dodji, Genichi.
Smesticu te u krevet.

664
01:22:48,285 --> 01:22:54,560
Nisam imao nimalo
mira od kada sam otisao,

665
01:22:54,760 --> 01:22:58,044
ali sam najzad kuci.

666
01:26:24,370 --> 01:26:27,871
Hjy, ima li koga?
Otvorite vrata!

667
01:26:30,717 --> 01:26:33,425
Ima li koga?
Otvorite.

668
01:26:39,679 --> 01:26:40,723
Seoski poglavica!

669
01:26:40,922 --> 01:26:43,728
Genjuro! Vratio si se?

670
01:26:44,113 --> 01:26:46,950
Hvala ti na dobrodi u mom izostanku.

671
01:26:50,140 --> 01:26:52,521
Tu si decace moj!

672
01:26:52,724 --> 01:26:54,888
Bio sam jako zabrinut
neznajuci gde ides.

673
01:26:55,530 --> 01:26:56,955
Tako sam srecan.

674
01:27:00,250 --> 01:27:01,620
Drago mi je.

675
01:27:02,388 --> 01:27:05,095
Decak sigurno zna da si se vratio.

676
01:27:06,406 --> 01:27:07,580
Miyagi.

677
01:27:13,327 --> 01:27:15,557
Sanjas li?

678
01:27:15,750 --> 01:27:16,957
Sanjam?

679
01:27:17,824 --> 01:27:20,945
Miyagi je ubila protivnicka vojska.

680
01:27:22,896 --> 01:27:24,353
Ubijena?

681
01:27:27,616 --> 01:27:32,357
Bila bi tako srecna da
te moze videti zivog i zdravog.

682
01:27:34,186 --> 01:27:35,871
Jadno stvorenje.

683
01:27:38,236 --> 01:27:41,042
Milostivi Buda...

684
01:27:45,763 --> 01:27:47,546
Od kako je umrla,

685
01:27:48,602 --> 01:27:51,244
starao sam se o tvom decaku.

686
01:27:52,015 --> 01:27:54,874
Uplasio sam se kada je sinoc nestao.

687
01:27:58,107 --> 01:28:00,880
Veza izmedju deteta
i roditelja je zaista jaka.

688
01:28:01,072 --> 01:28:05,248
Ali kako je mogao znati da si se vratio?

689
01:28:22,378 --> 01:28:25,368
Dodjavola s tim stvarima!

690
01:28:31,468 --> 01:28:36,949
Govorio sam ti, ali si bio isuvise glup
da bi me poslusao.

691
01:28:37,177 --> 01:28:40,809
Rat nas je izludeo sa ambicijom.

692
01:28:42,153 --> 01:28:44,698
Ne dozvoli da moja patnja bude uzaludna.

693
01:28:45,406 --> 01:28:47,983
Saberi se radi vredno.

694
01:29:08,434 --> 01:29:10,337
Zasto si morala da umres?

695
01:29:11,942 --> 01:29:15,030
Zasto, Miyagi?

696
01:29:32,833 --> 01:29:35,160
Nisam umrla.

697
01:29:35,863 --> 01:29:38,636
Ja sam uz tebe.

698
01:29:40,105 --> 01:29:43,356
Tvojim zabludama je dosao kraj.

699
01:29:44,921 --> 01:29:50,304
Opet si onaj stari,
na mestu u kom pripadas.

700
01:29:51,205 --> 01:29:54,609
Posao te ceka...

701
01:30:06,832 --> 01:30:09,410
kakva divna forma!

702
01:30:11,361 --> 01:30:17,734
Bilo mi je veliko zadovoljstvo
da ti pomazem oko izrade.

703
01:30:19,207 --> 01:30:22,045
Sve dok ne bude skroz peceno!

704
01:30:23,928 --> 01:30:26,287
Drvo za potpalu je spremno.

705
01:30:26,861 --> 01:30:29,918
Divlji vojnici su otisli.

706
01:30:30,434 --> 01:30:34,892
Tako da mozes da radis u miru.

707
01:30:39,970 --> 01:30:42,928
Toliko se stvari dogodilo.

708
01:30:45,552 --> 01:30:50,750
Konacno si postao covek
kakvog sam oduvek zelela.

709
01:30:51,485 --> 01:30:53,617
Ali tugo moja...

710
01:30:55,184 --> 01:30:59,610
Ja vise nisam medju zivima.

711
01:31:01,786 --> 01:31:05,255
Ali zivot je takav, predpostavljam.

712
01:31:25,516 --> 01:31:28,191
Mora da si umoran.
Odmori se malo.

713
01:31:38,177 --> 01:31:40,113
Uzmi malo, Genichi.
Dobro je.

714
01:31:40,410 --> 01:31:42,476
